      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW LONDON (4) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten half a length (22.74) behind MORAINE QUINN at this track. Top prospect. LILLY'S WISH (1) produced a moderate performance last time when sixth at Horsham over 410m behind Pay Up Sally (24.51) in a Grade 5. Placed at her previous run. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from seven starts. Has the ability to give this a shake. PAW OLYSLAGERS (6) was in the minors two back (22.62) at Ballarat but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Key player if finds best. ELEVENTH SCOTCH (7) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
